&lt;p&gt;1 -            t.join(maxTime);&lt;br/&gt;
 20 +            t.join(maxTime - now);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;so we don&apos;t wait System.currenTimeMillis anymore and that we would cycle ten times though all threads were &apos;dead&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
